reviewText: I honestly think this course will NOT prepare you for the certification exam. While the course is nicely and friendly, the questions on the certification exam are much more challenging than what is covered in this course. I would venture to say that the certification exam requires a much higher level of knowledge than what is covered in this course.

I really learned a lot about meta marketing through this course. Course content is informative and engaging. I applied some of the technique in my current organization for advertisement and use the matrix lerned from this course.
I would like to thank everyone who contributed to the success of this experiment. Through Coursera, we are able to spread tolerance and humanity while also providing a platform for knowledge.
El curso es muy útil. Se aprenden muchas cosas nuevas de la mano de verdaderos expertos.
Practical and detailed instruction. I will also take the exam 200-101 Meta Marketing Science.

yesterday I passed my Meta certification! Thank you for this prep-course! :) 
PS: currently waiting for my combined coursera/meta badge. hopefully it will arrive soon
Such an Amazing course, the instructors were all great.Thank you all
